Tucka-d tutlayt '''Taɛṛabt''' zɣ [[Tazunegzirt taɛṛabt]]. Ɣ tasut tiss 7 tga-d Taɛṛabt tutlayt n [[Lqʷran|lqquran]] ( Awal n rbbi ) n [[Lislam]] .

Tga Taεṛabt tutlayt tamaddudt ɣ 27 n tmizar tg ula tutlayt taɣlnawt ɣ [[Mali]], [[Sinigal]], d [[Ṣumal|Sumal]]. Tutlayt taεṛabt tettyura s ugmmay aεrab, tirra nns gi-s 28 iskkiln iyttyaran zɣ ufasi s uzlmaḍ. Tṭṭf kigan n tntalyin, mqqar d-kant tantaliyin ad tutlayt taεṛabt ur ar bahra ttmyarmasn imslɛṛabn ingratsn, amdya : taεṛabt alubnani ur iẓḍar ay-rms taεṛabt tamrrukit. 

Nẓḍaṛ ad nbḍu gr sin n timdyazin : tamdyazt n dat lislam, tamdyazt n dffir lislam, qqarn-as s tεṛabt "tajahilit".

== Tutlayt tunṣibt ==
Taɛrabt tafuṣḥit tga tutlayt tunṣibt ɣ 25 tmizar, aya ad-tt yujjan ad tg tutlayt tiss kraḍt dffir [[Tutlayt Tafransist|tafransist]] d [[Tutlayt Tanglizt|tanglizt]] 

* Tmizar n iɛrabn : [[Tagldit Tasaɛudit|Saɛudya]], [[Baḥrayn]], [[Juzur n Lqumur]], [[Djibuti]], [[Timizar iɛrabn imunn]], [[ɛiraq]], [[Urdun]], [[Kuwit]], [[Lubnan]], [[Ɛuman]], [[Filiṣṭin]], [[Qatar]], [[Somalya]], [[Sudan]], [[Surya]], [[Lyaman]] ;
* Tmizar n [[Tafriqt n ugafa|tfriqt n ugafa]] : [[Dzayr]], [[Miṣra]], [[Lmɣrib]], [[Muritanya]], [[Tuns]], [[Libya]] ;
* Tmizar yaḍn zun d [[Irytri]], [[Tcad]] ;

Tutlayt tunṣibt n tmazirt n [[Malṭa]], tutlayt tamalṭit, tga yat zɣ tantliwin n tutlayt taɛrabt.

== Amzruy ==
Taɛrabt tga tutlayt tasamit. Urtettuysawal Taɛrabt tafusḥit ɣ wass-ad walaynni llan sul ilsawn n taɛrabt ɣ timizar n agmud anammas n tafriqt n ugafa. 

